{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban animal farming for meat & dairy purposes and release animals into the wild",
        "additional_details": "We believe we should be looking to increase our vegan options. We feel humans should not be killing animals or farming them for animal-derived products that are only meant to be used by animals of their own species.",
        "background": "Ban animal farming for meat & dairy purposes, and release farm animals into the wild away from humans. They are a separate species from us, and we don't need to consume them or animal-derived products as we have other alternatives and meat and dairy free products on the market already.",
